data.title: Commons:Picture of the day/Unused featured pictures
data.text:
The following images appear to be featured pictures that have not yet been used as POTD.

Before nominating any of these images, please check manually that the image is actually featured and that it has not already been used.

This page is not automatically kept up to date. An up to date list can be obtained here.

Feel free to update this page, and also feel free to leave comments, questions and suggestions next to individual images. (Just prefix your comment with an "|", for eg File:African_penguins.jpg|I think we should have photos of penguins.)
